-- China Will Have as Much as $2 Trillion to Invest Abroad: Jiang
-- B y   R e b e c c a   P e n t y
-- 2012-09-06T22:04:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-06/china-will-have-as-much-as-2-trillion-to-invest-abroad-jiang.html
The Chinese economy is only just
coming to scale and will have $1 trillion to $2 trillion to
invest abroad over the next five to 10 years according to some
estimates, said  Wenran Jiang , director of the Canada-China
Energy & Environment Forum.  Jiang made his comments today at the Bloomberg Canada-Asia
Conference in Vancouver.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rebecca Penty in Calgary at 
